sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Gateway
    participant Sidecar as llm-d-routing-sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Allowlist as AllowlistValidator<br/>(in-process)
    participant Prefiller as Remote vLLM Prefiller<br/>variable port HTTP(S)
    participant Decoder as Local vLLM Decoder<br/>8001/TCP HTTP(S)

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL v2 Protocol)

    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Header: x-prefiller-host-port

    Sidecar->>Allowlist: Validate prefiller host<br/>against InferencePool pod IPs
    Allowlist-->>Sidecar: Allowed (or 403 Forbidden)

    Note over Sidecar: Wrap request with<br/>kv_transfer_params<br/>Set max_tokens=1<br/>Disable streaming

    Sidecar->>Prefiller: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP(S) Optional TLS 1.2+<br/>Modified prefill request

    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Prefill response<br/>KV transfer params:<br/>engine IDs, block IDs,<br/>host/port info

    Note over Sidecar: Extract KV transfer params<br/>Construct decode request<br/>with prefill metadata

    Sidecar->>Decoder: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP(S) Optional TLS 1.2+<br/>Decode request + KV params

    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streaming response<br/>(inference tokens)

    Sidecar-->>Client: Streaming response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Direct Passthrough (No Prefill Header)

    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>(no x-prefiller-host-port)

    Sidecar->>Decoder: Forward request as-is<br/>HTTP(S) localhost:8001<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+

    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Response<br/>(inference tokens)

    Sidecar-->>Client: Response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
